{"tid":380464,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"拒絕上車，Chamberlain更願參軍","createTime":"2017-08-30T06:42:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-31T06:32:17.000Z","uid":11512,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e953a43977b5c89e6c3b23df6e178bca91de5d01","tid":380464,"uid":11512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T06:42:08.000Z","msg":"合約只餘一年的Chamberlain25日拒絕了續約，隨即引起了車路士與利物浦的注意。前者在28日出價3500萬鎊，並且獲阿仙奴接受。但日前&lt;BBC&gt;及&lt;天空體育&gt;均傳出球員不願意加盟藍軍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://ichef.bbci.co.uk/onesport/cps/800/cpsprodpb/10B23/production/_97578386_oxlade-chamberlain_getty.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fonesport%2Fcps%2F800%2Fcpsprodpb%2F10B23%2Fproduction%2F_97578386_oxlade-chamberlain_getty.jpg&h=53168ceb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n按&lt;BBC&gt;報導，球員希望能在球隊擔任中場中的角色，而並非是翼衛。按照車路士的陣容配置，Chamberlain一旦加盟，很可能是與Moses競爭位置。因此，球員更希望投效紅軍。<br />\n<br />\n截止現時為止，利物浦並未報價，但一般相信價錢會教車路士低。而若果球員仍舊拒絕車路士的邀請，他將會繼續留效阿仙奴，待到明年合約完結後離開。"},{"pid":"c865ab7a3de77e5b6e33b5723a53faa37e7a42c7","tid":380464,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T06:43:47.000Z","msg":"屌奶星，比老鼠燈走咗"},{"pid":"faa31a71ec9a14713e7950358a4a89e0faf802c4","tid":380464,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T06:45:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2d48e496d6a4a65dcad95975ebf9ed0ef538ed0e","tid":380464,"uid":4652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T06:48:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌奶星，比老鼠燈走咗</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d008d9a5e26d5dea6d22b1a569dd9ebb3522df3","tid":380464,"uid":4586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T06:48:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌奶星，比老鼠燈走咗</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"